WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.190
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:04.470
joining us today. We are going to

00:00:04.480 --> 00:00:06.510
start praying

00:00:06.520 --> 00:00:08.310
more and more;

00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:10.749
that's what the Lord has

00:00:10.759 --> 00:00:12.789
told me to do and he told Diana to do

00:00:12.799 --> 00:00:13.950
the same thing.

00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:15.789
It's not really

00:00:15.799 --> 00:00:17.830
prophetic; some of the things I see, I

00:00:17.840 --> 00:00:20.070
feel like they're warnings. As watchmen

00:00:20.070 --> 00:00:20.080
and watchwomen

00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:22.750
and men of God,

00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:25.830
we're watchmen and we are going to start

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:28.630
praying against some of the things

00:00:28.640 --> 00:00:30.749
that the Lord has showed us. It's not

00:00:30.759 --> 00:00:32.709
just to tell you about it and just go,

00:00:32.719 --> 00:00:34.470
'Hey, sound the alarm,'and then do nothing

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:37.869
about it. We're called to change things,

00:00:37.879 --> 00:00:40.510
and prayer—that's our whole

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:43.310
slogan: Prayer Changes Things. We

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:45.470
believe in the power of prayer and we

00:00:45.480 --> 00:00:49.910
got our first picture today in the

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:51.990
mail because we told you all to send

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.549
your pictures to us so we could pray

00:00:54.559 --> 00:00:57.069
over your families. Whatever you are

00:00:57.079 --> 00:00:58.990
believing God for, write on

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:01.029
the back of the picture.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.030
Diana and I will pray over it right now.

00:01:06.030 --> 00:01:06.040
Write

00:01:06.040 --> 00:01:07.950
on the back, 'Hey, we

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:09.710
do not want this shown,'or, 'It's okay to

00:01:09.720 --> 00:01:11.830
share the

00:01:11.830 --> 00:01:11.840
picture,'because

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:13.190
some people don't want to be all over

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:14.550
the internet. But we're going to pray

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:16.429
for this family today.

00:01:16.439 --> 00:01:18.390
Her husband's dressed up in a

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.950
tuxedo,

00:01:20.950 --> 00:01:20.960
and

00:01:20.960 --> 00:01:22.310
they look like they're at a wedding;

00:01:22.320 --> 00:01:24.550
they look nice,

00:01:24.550 --> 00:01:24.560
a

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:26.789
very classy family.

00:01:26.799 --> 00:01:28.630
This woman says that her

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:31.870
son is wayward and he is not

00:01:31.880 --> 00:01:34.030
talking to the family anymore. It sounds

00:01:34.030 --> 00:01:34.040
like a

00:01:34.040 --> 00:01:35.749
pretty rough situation,

00:01:35.759 --> 00:01:37.550
but we're going to believe God that

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:39.429
he's going to turn around, that

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:41.630
he's coming home, and this wayward son is

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:43.429
going to be

00:01:43.439 --> 00:01:47.149
on fire for Jesus.

00:01:47.159 --> 00:01:50.429
The enemy is after the young people

00:01:50.439 --> 00:01:52.910
because they are going to be

00:01:52.920 --> 00:01:54.389
the forerunners of this great

00:01:54.399 --> 00:01:56.789
revival that's about to take place. When

00:01:56.799 --> 00:02:00.069
we go to these places

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:03.310
and drive around, I have an

00:02:03.320 --> 00:02:07.190
urgency for the college kids

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:09.070
because I know what God is about to do

00:02:09.080 --> 00:02:11.710
on these campuses. Someone mailed me

00:02:11.720 --> 00:02:14.750
something that showed

00:02:14.760 --> 00:02:16.470
some of the college campuses having

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:18.309
revivals.

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:22.910
It was all over

00:02:22.920 --> 00:02:25.430
several college campuses; they're having

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:28.430
major baptisms, salvations, and

00:02:28.430 --> 00:02:28.440
altar

00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:31.390
calls. Amazing stuff is going on.

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:34.869
I believe we're seeing the first

00:02:34.879 --> 00:02:37.229
fruits that will start to spring up. He

00:02:37.239 --> 00:02:40.149
told me March, April, and May that we would

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:42.470
start to see the first fruits of the

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:45.949
outpouring of the finances. It's

00:02:45.959 --> 00:02:48.710
already been a major thing that happened

00:02:48.720 --> 00:02:50.910
Friday. Now some people say that was a

00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:52.910
big nothingburger,

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:54.710
but

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:57.149
folks, we

00:02:57.159 --> 00:02:59.949
have a president that is

00:02:59.949 --> 00:02:59.959
pro-crypto,

00:02:59.959 --> 00:03:02.030
saying that we want to

00:03:02.040 --> 00:03:04.789
have a Bitcoin reserve.

00:03:04.789 --> 00:03:04.799
The

00:03:04.799 --> 00:03:07.910
last administration was

00:03:07.920 --> 00:03:10.710
trying to sue everybody and

00:03:10.710 --> 00:03:10.720
the

00:03:10.720 --> 00:03:14.190
SEC was after everything. It sounds to me

00:03:14.200 --> 00:03:16.350
like we have, for the first time, an

00:03:16.360 --> 00:03:19.190
administration saying, 'Hey, we want to

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:23.509
join this new platform of new

00:03:23.509 --> 00:03:23.519
technology.'That

00:03:23.519 --> 00:03:27.190
in itself is a miracle. Without

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:30.110
having some kind of big windfall of

00:03:30.110 --> 00:03:30.120
a financial

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.190
outpouring, we see the

00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:35.750
foundation

00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:39.309
being laid for the wealth of the sinner

00:03:39.319 --> 00:03:41.789
laid up for the righteous. We're

00:03:41.799 --> 00:03:43.630
seeing the first blades: we have the

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:46.190
blade, then the ear, then

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:48.110
the full manifestation, and then the

00:03:48.110 --> 00:03:48.120
crop—the

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:51.149
huge field of

00:03:51.159 --> 00:03:53.069
harvest.

00:03:53.079 --> 00:03:56.390
It has to start somewhere, and I

00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:58.509
believe we just saw a little

00:03:58.519 --> 00:04:01.910
blade poke up out of the dirt saying,

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:04.750
'Hello, I'm here.'That should get you

00:04:04.760 --> 00:04:07.949
excited.

00:04:07.949 --> 00:04:07.959
The

00:04:07.959 --> 00:04:10.789
last administration with

00:04:10.799 --> 00:04:12.750
Elizabeth

00:04:12.750 --> 00:04:12.760
Warren—she

00:04:12.760 --> 00:04:14.750
doesn't

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:16.749
like crypto and she's like, 'We're going

00:04:16.759 --> 00:04:18.749
to stop it, we're going to

00:04:18.759 --> 00:04:20.030
destroy

00:04:20.030 --> 00:04:20.040
it.'Here

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:22.350
we have

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:24.510
President Trump

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:30.110
saying,

00:04:30.120 --> 00:04:31.830
'Let's make America great again.'It is something

00:04:31.830 --> 00:04:31.840
to look forward to.

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:33.790
At least

00:04:33.790 --> 00:04:33.800
'Pocahontas'might

00:04:33.800 --> 00:04:35.430
be quiet for a little

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:38.550
bit in the SEC.

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:41.230
Praise the Lord, it is what it is, Diana.

00:04:41.240 --> 00:04:43.350
These people are evil.

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:45.070
They can't even stand up for a cancer

00:04:45.080 --> 00:04:47.830
patient.

00:04:51.039 --> 00:04:54.029
God help them all.

00:04:54.039 --> 00:04:56.070
Well, we're going to pray now.

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:57.510
The Lord said, 'Make five

00:04:57.520 --> 00:04:59.110
minutes, don't sit here and ramble

00:04:59.110 --> 00:04:59.120
on.'So

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:01.350
we're going to make

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:03.070
it just five minutes of talking and

00:05:03.080 --> 00:05:06.270
we're going to do a lot of praying.

00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:08.070
Let's get praying. We're going to

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:10.029
take communion with

00:05:10.039 --> 00:05:12.110
y'all. We're going

00:05:14.320 --> 00:05:16.070
into the throne room of God. This is

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:18.430
what we do in this household: we never

00:05:18.440 --> 00:05:20.110
enter into prayer without taking

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:22.830
communion first. I'm

00:05:22.840 --> 00:05:25.710
showing what is mine is

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:28.270
God's and what's God's is mine.

00:05:28.280 --> 00:05:30.590
Everything he has provided for me, I

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:32.830
receive it by the blood of the Lamb and

00:05:32.840 --> 00:05:34.510
by the word of our testimony. He has

00:05:34.520 --> 00:05:37.670
redeemed us, he set us free, and we

00:05:37.680 --> 00:05:40.950
enter into his throne boldly because of

00:05:40.960 --> 00:05:42.909
his son's blood and what he did

00:05:42.919 --> 00:05:45.550
for us on that beautiful cross.

00:05:45.560 --> 00:05:47.550
Thank you to whoever

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:50.029
sent these communion cups to us

00:05:50.029 --> 00:05:50.039
from

00:05:50.039 --> 00:05:53.230
Amazon.

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:01.590
You sent us two boxes;

00:06:01.600 --> 00:06:02.710
it's a blessing.

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:04.950
Father, we take this body

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:06.309
right now in the name of Jesus. If you just

00:06:06.319 --> 00:06:07.950
have a cracker, it's good;

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:12.430
people say that's disrespectful, but God

00:06:12.440 --> 00:06:14.550
knows your heart. I'll take a potato chip,

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:16.469
whatever I can, just to get close to

00:06:16.479 --> 00:06:18.270
the Father. It's what it represents in

00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:21.070
your heart. I come before him boldly.

00:06:21.080 --> 00:06:23.589
If it's a piece of bread or

00:06:23.599 --> 00:06:25.430
whatever,

00:06:25.440 --> 00:06:29.110
don't be religious; just

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:31.550
look at him and say, 'Jesus, I want to be

00:06:31.560 --> 00:06:35.070
close to you. I want to know you

00:06:35.080 --> 00:06:39.309
more than I know my past

00:06:39.319 --> 00:06:43.589
memories. I'm desperate for

00:06:46.189 --> 00:06:46.199
change.'Some

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:51.950
people can't afford much, but

00:06:51.960 --> 00:06:55.469
if you do this daily and you seek him

00:06:55.479 --> 00:06:58.189
daily, and you sow when he tells you to

00:06:58.189 --> 00:06:58.199
sow,

00:06:58.199 --> 00:07:01.749
and you give, and it shall be given

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:03.430
unto you—good measure, pressed down,

00:07:03.430 --> 00:07:03.440
shaken

00:07:03.440 --> 00:07:05.790
together, and running over, will

00:07:05.800 --> 00:07:08.710
men give into your bosom. I believe he

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:10.710
said in Malachi that he

00:07:10.720 --> 00:07:12.710
would rebuke the devourer for your sake,

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:15.830
even if it's just a penny.

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:21.230
I believe what he says more

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:22.710
than I believe my

00:07:22.720 --> 00:07:24.790
circumstances. Regardless of what

00:07:33.039 --> 00:07:36.469
I have in

00:07:36.479 --> 00:07:37.350
the

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:40.629
bank, the Bible says that I'll be the

00:07:40.639 --> 00:07:43.430
lender and not the

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:49.110
borrower—that

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:53.110
I will be able to lend to the

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:55.149
nations.

00:07:55.159 --> 00:07:57.830
To be able to lend to a

00:07:57.840 --> 00:08:00.029
nation is substantial.

00:08:08.360 --> 00:08:11.189
It needs to be hundreds of

00:08:11.199 --> 00:08:13.230
millions of dollars in the bank to say,

00:08:13.240 --> 00:08:16.629
'I'm a lender to

00:08:16.639 --> 00:08:18.950
nations.'The

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:21.510
United States gives

00:08:21.520 --> 00:08:23.589
money to people, and you think about how

00:08:23.599 --> 00:08:26.550
much money that is—it's billions.

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:28.790
That's exceedingly abundantly above

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:30.230
all that you dare ask or think. But how

00:08:30.240 --> 00:08:32.070
do you start there? You start with

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:35.149
a seed, and

00:08:36.839 --> 00:08:40.750
a seed brings forth increase:

00:08:40.760 --> 00:08:44.470
some thirty, some sixty, and some

00:08:44.470 --> 00:08:44.480
hundredfold.

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:46.350
It's all

00:08:46.350 --> 00:08:46.360
in

00:08:46.360 --> 00:08:49.190
the ground you're sowing into. If

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:51.710
you're sowing into bad ground, don't

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:54.269
expect a big harvest.

00:09:22.279 --> 00:09:24.990
A farmer doesn't sow into

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:27.509
bad ground; he

00:09:27.509 --> 00:09:27.519
sows

00:09:27.519 --> 00:09:30.550
into manure or

00:09:30.560 --> 00:09:33.310
fertilized ground that's going to reap

00:09:33.320 --> 00:09:35.230
back. So that's what we're going to do

00:09:35.240 --> 00:09:37.430
today.

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:39.949
Now Father, I thank you for their

00:09:39.959 --> 00:09:42.310
ground. I thank you that whatever

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:45.870
they put their hands to will prosper.

00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:48.069
Father, we take authority over the spirit

00:09:48.079 --> 00:09:51.949
of poverty, lack, not enough, and barely

00:09:51.959 --> 00:09:55.190
getting by. We break your stronghold off

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:57.949
of them in the name of Jesus and we say:

00:09:57.959 --> 00:10:01.710
let go of their money now in

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:05.670
Jesus'name.

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:08.389
Father, I thank you

00:10:08.399 --> 00:10:10.870
that you said you would provide

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:12.910
everything according to your riches and

00:10:12.920 --> 00:10:15.910
glory by Christ Jesus. All our needs are

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:18.150
met.

00:10:18.160 --> 00:10:19.710
Father, we thank you that it's

00:10:19.720 --> 00:10:22.710
not just about finances, it's about our

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:25.949
health.

00:10:25.959 --> 00:10:29.430
You

00:10:29.440 --> 00:10:31.790
took it all on the cross for us.

00:10:38.680 --> 00:10:41.230
The

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:44.750
chastisement of our peace was upon you

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:48.110
and with your stripes we're healed.

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:50.790
Lord, we take up this body right now.

00:10:50.800 --> 00:10:52.670
You were wounded for our transgressions

00:10:52.670 --> 00:10:52.680
and

00:10:52.680 --> 00:10:54.670
bruised for our iniquities,

00:10:57.760 --> 00:10:59.949
and we

00:10:59.959 --> 00:11:02.870
believe we receive today all the

00:11:02.880 --> 00:11:06.030
ills that as we take this body into our

00:11:06.040 --> 00:11:08.190
body, we're healed, whole, and well in

00:11:08.200 --> 00:11:10.430
the name of Jesus.

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:16.670
Now Lord, you

00:11:16.680 --> 00:11:18.670
said to make much of the blood and the

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:21.710
blood will make much of you. We

00:11:35.440 --> 00:11:38.150
plead the blood of Jesus

00:11:38.160 --> 00:11:41.430
over our families and over our sins.

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:43.590
We thank you that the

00:11:43.600 --> 00:11:46.430
blood washes it all away

00:11:46.440 --> 00:11:49.470
today. When we

00:11:49.480 --> 00:11:51.509
confess our sins, you're faithful and

00:11:51.519 --> 00:11:53.670
just to forgive us and

00:11:53.680 --> 00:11:56.069
cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:11:56.079 --> 00:11:58.509
We plead the blood of Jesus

00:11:58.519 --> 00:12:00.629
from the top of our head to the soles of

00:12:00.639 --> 00:12:03.190
our feet.

00:12:13.560 --> 00:12:15.230
Take communion the way

00:12:15.230 --> 00:12:15.240
you

00:12:15.240 --> 00:12:17.189
like;

00:12:18.440 --> 00:12:20.949
there's no

00:12:20.959 --> 00:12:23.030
right or wrong way,

00:12:23.040 --> 00:12:25.389
there's only seeking

00:12:25.399 --> 00:12:29.590
Jesus. Find

00:12:29.600 --> 00:12:30.949
a

00:12:30.959 --> 00:12:33.870
relationship, not

00:12:39.110 --> 00:12:39.120
religion.

00:12:45.320 --> 00:12:47.550
So, Father, we lift up Christian

00:12:47.560 --> 00:12:49.829
before you right now.

00:12:49.839 --> 00:12:52.670
Christian, you're coming home in

00:12:52.670 --> 00:12:52.680
Jesus'name.

00:12:52.680 --> 00:12:55.870
We speak for this family to

00:12:55.880 --> 00:12:59.189
be reunited. Satan, take your

00:12:59.199 --> 00:13:02.030
hands off Christian and his family.

00:13:15.279 --> 00:13:17.509
I thank you, Father, that you've

00:13:17.519 --> 00:13:19.269
called us to the kingdom for such a time

00:13:19.279 --> 00:13:21.350
as this to pray over the ones that are

00:13:21.360 --> 00:13:22.829
lost

00:13:22.829 --> 00:13:22.839
and

00:13:22.839 --> 00:13:25.629
wayward. As a point of contact

00:13:25.639 --> 00:13:27.670
for all the other ones

00:13:27.680 --> 00:13:29.269
on this channel who

00:13:29.269 --> 00:13:29.279
are wayward,

00:13:29.279 --> 00:13:30.990
we're

00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:33.470
believing with you right now that Satan

00:13:33.480 --> 00:13:35.910
has to let go of those unsaved loved

00:13:35.920 --> 00:13:38.030
ones right now. We call them into the

00:13:38.040 --> 00:13:41.189
kingdom of God.

00:13:55.920 --> 00:13:58.310
I thank you that

00:13:58.320 --> 00:14:00.829
their eyes are no longer blinded by the

00:14:00.839 --> 00:14:04.110
demonic. This

00:14:04.120 --> 00:14:06.069
will be a time

00:14:06.079 --> 00:14:09.550
of a great turnaround

00:14:09.560 --> 00:14:12.470
in families.

00:14:19.680 --> 00:14:22.590
We bind these demonic spirits off

00:14:22.600 --> 00:14:25.430
the families and say you will

00:14:25.430 --> 00:14:25.440
go

00:14:25.440 --> 00:14:28.430
thus far and no further.

00:14:42.680 --> 00:14:45.790
We call

00:14:45.800 --> 00:14:48.670
for

00:14:48.680 --> 00:14:50.550
a

00:14:50.560 --> 00:14:52.350
turnaround in your marriages,

00:14:52.360 --> 00:14:54.509
your children, and

00:14:54.519 --> 00:14:55.710
your

00:14:55.720 --> 00:14:57.030
